  TITLE     Purification and characterization of a novel enzyme, arylalkyl acylamidase, from Pseudomonas putida Sc2.
  JOURNAL   Eur. J. Biochem. 209 (1992) 375-82.
  ORGANISM  Pseudomonas putida
